regions.title: Handgun and person holding it
regions.description: This region highlights the area where a man is holding a handgun, which is the main threat in the image. The cells are highly overlapped, indicating high confidence in this threat region.

summary: The primary threat identified is the handgun being held by the man in the lower right of the image. All high-confidence cells in that region have been retained. Lower-confidence cells unrelated to the threat were removed.
